- ğŸ“Š Automated RÂ² calculation for model comparison
- ğŸ”¥ Activation energy (Eâ‚) and pre-exponential factor (kâ‚€) determination
- ğŸ“ˆ Built-in visualization for concentration-time profiles and Arrhenius plots
- ğŸ” Optimal reaction order identification

